{"type":"message","id":"2426be66","parentId":"b5388c4f","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:17:33.839Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978 空闲检测自主学习] 请检测当前是否有活跃对话（查询 sessions_list）。如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息），则执行自主学习：\n\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n如果有活跃对话，直接回复\"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\nCurrent time: Friday, March 27th, 2026 — 10:17 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-27 14:17 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774621053836}}
{"type":"message","id":"a01be085","parentId":"2426be66","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:17:39.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job task. I need to:\n1. Check if there are active sessions (query sessions_list)\n2. If no active sessions in the last 5 minutes, perform autonomous learning\n3. If there are active sessions, just reply that there's an active conversation\n\nLet me first check the sessions list.","thinkingSignature":"c44c02ed63d5482c3195f6006fa93c850b45f05fb30377788eb84f6d40f23d8a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s6oewukrp7k4_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":104,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":172,"totalTokens":44394,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0.00002064,"total":0.00150597}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774621053838}}
