{"type":"message","id":"d40c4aa0","parentId":"0e5ff517","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:19:33.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task is complete. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"cbc00b72e54113b951e3438896bdaf9b9b3a90595512e684f8a8bcd104848020"},{"type":"text","text":"**空闲自主学习完成 ✅**\n\n无活跃对话，执行了以下学习任务：\n\n**搜索范围**：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026最新政策动态\n2. 智能安防行业 2026发展趋势\n3. IT运维服务行业 2026趋势\n4. 网络系统集成行业 2026趋势\n\n**整理关键信息（5条）**：\n1. **AI全面渗透**：所有领域从\"被动响应\"向\"主动预判/预测自愈\"转变\n2. **融合架构成主流**：AIoT+边缘计算+零信任+SDN/NFV组合方案占43%千万级项目\n3. **服务化转型**：运维及增值服务成为主要收入来源\n4. **政策红利**：数字化转型专项补贴最高"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6205,"output":0,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50186,"cost":{"input":0.0018614999999999999,"output":0,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031809299999999998}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1774621167420,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted."}}
